{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df326543ba","title":"关于应说服红卫兵让王任重就医的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"afcd7e9283","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":2,"articleId":"df326543ba"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"8b05ac46d8","name":"王任重","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"19d8a618b5","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"df326543ba","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王任重，原任中共中央文化革命小组副组长、中南局第一书记、湖北省委第一书记，1967年1月受到错误批判后被打倒。"},{"id":"ea415ba7fc","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"df326543ba","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在王任重的妻子萧慧纳1967年1月29日给毛泽东的信上。信中说，王任重病重垂危，现被撤斗，不知去处，朝不保夕，请求给予治疗。2月3日，中共中央在给湖北省委并武汉军区党委的电报中指出：“王任重最近以来病情加重。为了使他能进一步检查错误，中央常委和中央文革小组建议能让王就医一段时间，红卫兵有事，视王病情许可，随叫随到。请武汉军区党委协助省委办理此事。”"},{"id":"9311e156ee","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"df326543ba","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林，指林彪，在中共八届十一中全会上继续当选为中央政治局常委，不久被称中央副主席。周，指周恩来。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8f5e7aa59d","type":"title","text":"关于应说服红卫兵让王任重“就医的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"df326543ba"},{"id":"19d8a618b5","type":"paragraph","text":"林、周阅后，交文革小组商处。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"df326543ba"},{"id":"ea415ba7fc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"df326543ba"},{"id":"9311e156ee","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"df326543ba"},{"id":"fcf2184386","type":"paragraph","text":"我意应说服红卫兵，让他就医。红卫兵有事，视王病情许可，随叫随到。","index":4,